        <p> We spent the rest of the day comfortably with splashes, sunbathing and doing nothing. In the evening it went to the delicious buffet as usual. This time we even had company: Hauke &#8203;&#8203;from Bad Schwartau was sitting with us at the table. He is alone in Tenerife and we got into conversation while eating when he turned out that he lives around the corner with us. The world is sometimes small! </p>
        <p> Another sunny and relaxed day of vacation comes to an end - that's exactly how we love it. </p>
